What Are High Converting Ads?
High converting ads are advertisements that persuade a large percentage of viewers to take a desired action, such as:
•	Filling out a lead form
•	Making a purchase
•	Booking a demo
•	Downloading an app
•	Subscribing to a service
The success of an ad is measured using the conversion rate:
Conversion Rate = (Conversions ÷ Total Clicks) × 100
A high converting ad does not just attract attention—it convinces users to act.
