Step 8: Implement Smart Targeting & Retargeting
Smart Targeting Methods
•	Lookalike audiences
•	In-market users
•	Custom intent audiences
•	Website visitors
Retargeting Strategy
Retarget users who:
•	Visited your website
•	Added to cart
•	Watched your video
•	Opened your form but didn’t submit
Retargeting ads often convert 3–5x higher than cold traffic ads.
________________________________________
Step 9: A/B Test Everything
Never assume what works. Test it.
You should test:
•	Headlines
•	Images vs videos
•	CTA buttons
•	Landing page layout
•	Form length
•	Offers
Run each test for at least 7–14 days before making conclusions.
Small improvements in conversion rate can lead to massive profit increases at scale.
________________________________________
Step 10: Track the Right Metrics
Do not focus only on clicks.
Key Metrics for High Converting Ads
•	Conversion rate
•	Cost per conversion
•	Return on ad spend (ROAS)
•	Bounce rate
•	Time on page
•	Funnel drop-off rate
Use tools like Google Analytics, Meta Ads Manager, and CRM dashboards.
